\
The Wormwood Diaries were encoded to provide the greatest specificity possible among the concepts provided. Users will be able to search among standard weather codes, names, places mentioned, and by multiple kinds of date formats, alongside quotes, titles, and other media mentions. The goal with this encoding strategy is to allow a corresponding webpage transformation the power to distill this information into tangible formats for users (e.g., a timeline of weather throughout the journals\'92 span).\
